metadata.name: FLOREVER COLORFUL
metadata.description:
This Plumeria photographed in Bermuda in 2008 has been re-rendered with AI to create a mystical and brilliant MintPass for my upcoming floral photography collection.

The FLOREVER COLORFUL MintPass will create a stackable multiplier for the Presale list as well as a stackable multiplier for discounted mint pricing.  Multipliers are stackable up to a quantity of 10.
